casebody.head_matter:
DEPARTMENT OF COMMERCE, et al., petitioners,
v.
UNITED STATES DISTRICT COURT FOR the SOUTHERN DISTRICT OF NEW YORK, et al.; and Department of Commerce, et al., petitioners,
v.
United States District Court for the Southern District of New York, et al.
No. 18-557.
Supreme Court of the United States
June 28, 2019.
Case remanded to the United States Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit with instructions to vacate that court's orders dated September 25, 2018 and October 9, 2018. See United States v. Munsingwear, Inc., 340 U.S. 36, 71 S.Ct. 104, 95 L.Ed. 36 (1950).
